Reasoning: The paper discusses challenges related to visual analysis of humans, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of machine learning techniques and the availability of public resources suggest that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on human-computer interaction and the use of gesture recognition suggest that the paper may also belong to the sub-category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the mention of preprints of papers suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-category of multimedia (cs.MM).
